title: Immediate! Spacious 2bd 2ba downtown high rise w/city views
posting_body: ['Spacious 2bd 2ba high rise corner apartment in West Downtown Minneapolis with city views.', 'Master suite with full bath and huge walk-in closet, in-unit laundry, pantry, linen closet, extra storage, dishwasher.', 'Open floorplan.', 'Did I mention all the closets?', 'All utilities except for electric and cable/internet included.', 'One covered garage space included in listed price, limited additional garage spaces available for purchase.', 'Cats allowed for additional pet fee (no dogs).', 'Access to all Laurel Village amenities <URL>/', 'Building has pool, hot tub, sauna, fitness center, party room, and massive rooftop space featuring grills, sundeck, and bocce court with amazing skyline views.', 'You have Lunds across the street, short walk to parks, restaurants, business, sports, music, and theater.', 'I have loved living here and only moved because I bought a house.', 'You will be taking over my existing lease through Dec 31st.', 'NOT a sublease, it will be all yours!', 'Laurel Village requires a credit and background check.', 'If approved, I will reimburse all transfer/application fees.', 'Prorated rent available for partial first month', 'Laurel Village allows you to paint a custom accent wall in each room.', "I painted the walls back to approved beige color and left you with the extra beige paint for your future use (it's kind of expensive).", 'I replaced all the bulbs with high-efficiency LED as well.']
